00:18:53,614 --> 00:19:01,058
So the end goal that we wanted was to provide a career guidance for the mentee, give them

355
00:19:01,238 --> 00:19:03,920
advice and help with their portfolio development.

356
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:08,162
You know, if they came to us with a portfolio, we'd give them feedback on how to strengthen

357
00:19:08,202 --> 00:19:08,262
it.

358
00:19:08,702 --> 00:19:13,125
And a lot of that would come based on what jobs they were actually looking to get.

359
00:19:14,165 --> 00:19:18,387
Someone's portfolio might look different if they were going for a pure narrative design

360
00:19:18,407 --> 00:19:19,888
job versus a pure writing job.

361
00:19:20,609 --> 00:19:25,434
So we wanted to kind of educate them on the differences so that they could scale their

362
00:19:25,474 --> 00:19:29,878
samples accordingly and also just provide ongoing support as they needed it.

