00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:33,781
So my experience coming in, as I mentioned,

364
00:19:34,301 --> 00:19:36,702
I had been doing informational interviews

365
00:19:36,762 --> 00:19:39,163
and sort of mining my network as much as possible

366
00:19:39,243 --> 00:19:40,884
to try to figure out who to talk to

367
00:19:41,144 --> 00:19:42,905
and who's already doing the job

