00:19:53,690 --> 00:19:55,070
once they told me about the program,

373
00:19:55,631 --> 00:19:58,153
was a couple of writing samples,

374
00:19:59,194 --> 00:20:01,457
preferably a teleplay if I had one,

375
00:20:01,737 --> 00:20:05,581
but something that I thought represented my range

376
00:20:05,862 --> 00:20:07,844
and my abilities, so that they could kind of see

